name: Protocol Failure
Lore: '''Oh my! Oh, uh, I''m, I''m terribly sorry. I. . . I didn''t mean to intrude. No, no, no, please don''t get up. No!''',
Text: 'Deploy on a site to cancel a Force drain there. Vader is deploy -1 here. At end of your turn, place this Effect in Lost Pile. OR At any time, target a unique (•) [Episode I] droid. Opponent chooses: deploy on droid (its game text is canceled), or place this Effect in Lost Pile (you may take any one card into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle). (Immune to Control.)',
